          <p class='first-para'>
            It could be &#x00A3;30,000 to &#x00A3;40,000.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0665P0-04542'>
        <a name='S5LV0665P0_20041018_GCR_141'>  </a>
